- `Validate()` - Validates that only one of BearerToken, BasicAuth, and BearerTokenFile is configured
- `SetDirectory(dir string)` - Joins any relative file paths with dir
- `UnmarshalYAML()` / `UnmarshalJSON()` - Configuration unmarshaling
- `String()` - String representation

---

